ASMARA, Eritrea, January 6, 2023/APO Group/ --
                                                        
                            His Holiness Abune Petros, Archbishop of the Eritrean Tewahdo Orthodox Church, gave benediction in connection with Christmas.


                                His Holiness Abune Petros wished peace and prosperity to the Eritrean people
                            

Abune Petros gave a detailed briefing on the background of the Holiday and wished Happy Christmas to the Eritrean people inside the country and abroad as well as to the Eritrean Defense Forces.

Abune Petros also called on the faithful to support families of martyrs and extend hands to the disadvantaged nationals.

Finally, His Holiness Abune Petros wished peace and prosperity to the Eritrean people.